online harassment is something most people have faced at some point regardless of their views on ethics in games journalism .
its a really tough problem because its a big problem it is far reaching it has many different forms .
the scope of the problem can discourage people from trying to fight it often this leads to thinking what can i do im just one person .
you arent just one person there are many of us and we all have voices but more than that we have resources experience and passion .
you arent alone in this youre never alone in this .

we have crashoverridenw an invaluable resource that provides emotional support for targets of harassment .
both of these organizations have been created to address different aspects of very real problems that affect all of us .
